      <title>特朗普将接待共和党领导人，因为早期行动将颠覆华盛顿</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-enters-day-two-after-flurry-of-orders-pardons-on-day-one</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统在白宫的第一天将进行高层国会磋商和高调的基础设施公告，他开始制定第二任期的立法和政治策略。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/trump-enters-day-two-after-flurry-of-orders-pardons-on-day-one</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 12:15:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽约州州长霍楚尔将在 2520 亿美元预算草案中详细说明减税措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/ny-gov-hochul-to-detail-tax-cuts-in-252-billion-draft-budget</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约州州长凯西·霍楚尔 (D) 周二公布了一项 2520 亿美元的支出计划，其中包括削减所得税和扩大社会保障网，因为该州面临着共和党控制的联邦政府带来的潜在不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/ny-gov-hochul-to-detail-tax-cuts-in-252-billion-draft-budget</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 11:00:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国寻求补贴天然气库存补充，欧洲天然气价格飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/european-gas-prices-swing-as-trump-lifts-ban-on-new-lng-exports</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在德国表示可能为天然气储存设施的补充提供补贴后，欧洲天然气价格大幅上涨，刺激了燃料的现货需求，并进一步推高了季节性价差。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-21/european-gas-prices-swing-as-trump-lifts-ban-on-new-lng-exports</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 21 Jan 2025 07:32:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的人工智能计划在关税基调下提振股市：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普在贸易问题上表现好于预期，人们越来越多地猜测他的政策将进一步提振美国企业，股市随之上涨。债券收益率继续回落，摆脱近期飙升的局面。美元波动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 22:26:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚电信资费上调 50% 后 MTN 股价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/nigeria-agrees-50-telecom-price-hike-after-lobbying</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚政府将电信资费提高 50%，以抵消奈拉暴跌和通胀飙升的影响，此后 MTN Nigeria Communications Plc 的股价大幅上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-20/nigeria-agrees-50-telecom-price-hike-after-lobbying</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 Jan 2025 18:12:09 GMT</pubDate>
